Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object detection and 3D position estimation using images from a monocular camera. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper focuses on traffic control in the context of autonomous vehicles. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a deep structural regression network for detecting the spatial arrangement of keypoints on a traffic cone. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with perception for autonomous driving. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as it is not directly related to the content of the paper.
